<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            padding: 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 280px;
        }
        .orb {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(40px);
            opacity: 0.5;
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .orb-1 {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            top: -40px;
            right: -40px;
            animation-delay: 0s;
        }
        .orb-2 {
            width: 140px;
            height: 140px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fa709a 0%, #fee140 100%);
            bottom: -20px;
            left: -20px;
            animation-delay: 2s;
        }
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-15px) scale(1.08); }
        }
        .lock-animation {
            position: absolute;
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: lockFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .lock-1 { top: 25%; left: 20%; animation-delay: 0s; }
        .lock-2 { top: 65%; left: 75%; animation-delay: 1.5s; }
        .lock-3 { top: 45%; right: 15%; animation-delay: 3s; }
        @keyframes lockFloat {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(-30px); }
        }
        .header-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 40px;
        }
        .icon-wrapper {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); }
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 64px;
        }
        .header-title {
            font-size: 38px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        .header-subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 50px 40px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin: 0 0 30px 0;
        }
        .otp-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9ff 0%, #fff5f8 100%);
            border: 2px solid #f093fb;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .otp-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(240, 147, 251, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes rotate {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        .otp-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #999999;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .otp-note {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #999999;
            margin: 20px 0 0 0;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background: #fff9e6;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .warning-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .warning-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666666;
            margin: 0;
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            line-height: 1.6;
            width: calc(100% - 40px);
        }
        .expiry-info {
            background: #f8f9fc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .expiry-label {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #999999;
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .expiry-time {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #e0e0e0, transparent);
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fc;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #999999;
            margin: 5px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .security-tip {
            background: #e8f5e9;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .security-tip-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2e7d32;
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        }
        .security-tip-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #558b2f;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
            <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
            <div class="lock-animation lock-1"></div>
            <div class="lock-animation lock-2"></div>
            <div class="lock-animation lock-3"></div>
            
            <div class="header-content">
                <div class="icon-wrapper">
                    <span class="icon">üîê</span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="header-title">Password Reset</h1>
                <p class="header-subtitle">Secure your account</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="greeting">Hello {{name}},</h2>
            
            <p class="message">
                We received a request to reset your password. Use the verification code below to complete the process:
            </p>
            
            <div class="otp-section">
                <p class="otp-label">Your Verification Code</p>
                <p class="otp-code">{{otp}}</p>
                <p class="otp-note">Enter this code to reset your password</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="expiry-info">
                <p class="expiry-label">‚è∞ Code Expires At</p>
                <p class="expiry-time">{{expiresAt}} UTC</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning-box">
                <span class="warning-icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</span>
                <p class="warning-text">
                    <strong>Didn't request this?</strong> If you didn't ask to reset your password, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-tip">
                <p class="security-tip-title">üõ°Ô∏è Security Tip</p>
                <p class="security-tip-text">
                    Never share your verification codes with anyone. Our team will never ask for your password or verification code.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p class="message" style="text-align: center; color: #999999; font-size: 14px;">
                Need help? Contact our support team ‚Äì we're here for you!
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p class="footer-text">
                <strong>Sent with security in mind ‚ù§Ô∏è</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="footer-text">
                This is an automated security email. Please do not reply.
            </p>
            <p class="footer-text" style="margin-top: 15px; color: #cccccc;">
                ¬© 2025 All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>